#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Udāyivagga"
msgstr "3. With Udāyī"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 22. Bojjhaṅgadesanāsutta → desanāsuttaṃ (bj) | desanā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Bojjhaṅgadesanāsutta"
msgstr "22. A Teaching on the Awakening Factors"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.22:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅge desessāmi;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.22:1.2"
msgid "taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn46.22:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā?"
msgstr "And what are the seven awakening factors?"

msgctxt "sn46.22:1.4"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.22:1.5"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā”ti."
msgstr "These are the seven awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.22:1.6"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
